'''新西兰商业、创新和就业部'''（{{lang-en|Ministry of Business, Innovation and Employment}}，简称MBIE，{{lang-mi|Hīkina Whakatutuki}}）是[[新西兰|新西兰]]的一个公共服务部门，负责提出“政策、服务、建议和法规”，对新西兰的经济生产和商业增长做出贡献。<ref name="NZgovt">{{cite web| url=https://www.govt.nz/organisations/ministry-of-business-innovation-and-employment/| title=Ministry of Business, Innovation and Employment| publisher=New Zealand Government| access-date=2020-11-20| archive-date=2021-02-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220070039/https://www.govt.nz/organisations/ministry-of-business-innovation-and-employment/| dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
MBIE成立于2012年1月，由建筑和住房部、劳工部、经济发展部和科学与创新部合并而成。

2018年10月，MBIE的住房和社会政策、基金及监管职能被移交给新成立的住房和城市发展部。<ref name="HUD Factsheet">{{cite web |title=HUD Factsheet 1 October 2018 |url=https://www.hud.govt.nz/assets/About-HUD/HUD-Factsheet-1-October-2018.pdf |publisher=Ministry of Housing and Urban Development |accessdate=1 February 2019 |archive-date=2019-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122040639/https://www.hud.govt.nz/assets/About-HUD/HUD-Factsheet-1-October-2018.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 组织 ==
MBIE设有五个副行政总裁，分别负责移民、企业管治与资讯、建筑与资源和市场、劳工与科学和企业、市场服务。

